item.title: Happy December!
item.description:
Happy December!

November flew by so quickly and winter is soon upon us. It was a pretty low-key month, and we mainly focused on getting things together for our annual Advent devotional. Every year, Rick (our lead pastor) puts together five devotionalsâ€”one for each Sunday leading up to Christmas. This year, he decided to do one for each day! Much of our time was spent creating header images, copy editing, and a bit of writing here and there.
